data.description: Come check out this beautiful, move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in the highly desired community of Belmont. As you enter the foyer you will notice the 18x18 tile throughout the main living areas. The kitchen features amazing 42” espresso cabinets, granite countertops and a center island with bar seating and hanging pendant lighting. ALL GE appliances are included with this property, even the WASHER and DRYER. You will also notice NEW PAINT in the living, kitchen, foyer and bathroom areas. All bedrooms have BRAND NEW water proof Larkmead Oak laminate flooring! No carpet here! The master bathroom features a walk-in glass shower, double sinks, and a large walk-in closet. This home also comes with corrugated steel Hurricane Panels and a Hybrid Water Heater which is rated 2-3 times more energy efficient than standard tank models. Sitting on a lot with a conservation view you do not need to worry about rear neighbors as the backyard faces Bullfrog Creek Natural Preserve. Belmont has TONS of amenities like walking trails, multiple playgrounds, basketball court, a gorgeous resort-style pool and two tennis courts! All that with a LOW HOA! Conveniently located near I-75, multiple schools, grocery stores and several amazing restaurants! Schedule your private showing today!
